     !(x b)::t. ITSET f s (f x b) = f x (ITSET f s b)``,
  completeInduct_on `CARD s` >>
  rule_assum_tac(SIMP_RULE bool_ss [GSYM RIGHT_FORALL_IMP_THM, AND_IMP_INTRO]) >>
